    "viewsWelcome.welcome.state":"GitLens 11 is powerful, feature rich, and highly customizable to meet your needs. You can use the GitLens Welcome experience to get setup quickly.\n\n[Welcome (Quick Setup)](command:gitlens.showWelcomePage \"Opens the GitLens Welcome (Quick Setup)\")\n\nFor more options, run [GitLens: Open Settings](command:gitlens.showSettingsPage \"Opens the GitLens Interactive Settings\") from the Command Palette to open the interactive GitLens settings editor.",
    "viewsWelcome.welcome.view":"[GitLens views](command:gitlens.showSettingsPage%23views) are shown on the Source Control side bar, by default. Run [GitLens: Set Views Layout](command:gitlens.setViewsLayout \"Changes the GitLens Views Layout\") from the Command Palette to switch to an alternate side bar layout, or drag & drop them.",
    "viewsWelcome.welcome.close":"[Close](command:gitlens.closeWelcomeView \"Closes the Welcome view\")",
    "viewsWelcome.searchAndCompare.searchcommit":"Search for commits by [message](command:gitlens.views.searchAndCompare.searchCommits?%7B%22search%22%3A%7B%22pattern%22%3A%22message%3A%22%7D%2C%22prefillOnly%22%3Atrue%7D), [author](command:gitlens.views.searchAndCompare.searchCommits?%7B%22search%22%3A%7B%22pattern%22%3A%22author%3A%22%7D%2C%22prefillOnly%22%3Atrue%7D), [SHA](command:gitlens.views.searchAndCompare.searchCommits?%7B%22search%22%3A%7B%22pattern%22%3A%22commit%3A%22%7D%2C%22prefillOnly%22%3Atrue%7D), [file](command:gitlens.views.searchAndCompare.searchCommits?%7B%22search%22%3A%7B%22pattern%22%3A%22file%3A%22%7D%2C%22prefillOnly%22%3Atrue%7D), or [changes](command:gitlens.views.searchAndCompare.searchCommits?%7B%22search%22%3A%7B%22pattern%22%3A%22change%3A%22%7D%2C%22prefillOnly%22%3Atrue%7D)\n\n[Search Commits...](command:gitlens.views.searchAndCompare.searchCommits)",
    "viewsWelcome.kylincommitsRelevant":"User can view commits details by [show commit view](commaiew?%7B%22search%22%3A%7B%22pattern%22%3A%22message%3A%22%7D%2C%22prefillOnly%22%3Atrue%7D), [Search for commit in Side Bar](command:gitlens.showCommitInView?%7B%22search%22%3A%7B%22pattern%22%3A%22author%3A%22%7D%2C%22prefillOnly%22%3Atrue%7D),or [Show file commits details](command:gitlens.showQuickCommitFileDetails?%7B%22search%22%3A%7B%22pattern%22%3A%22commit%3A%22%7D%2C%22prefillOnly%22%3Atrue%7D),\n\n[Show Single File History](command:kylin.viewfilehistory)\n\n[Show Commits Per Author](command:kylin.viewCommits)",
    "viewsWelcome.searchAndCompare.compare":"Compare a <branch, tag, or ref> with another <branch, tag, or ref>\n\n[Compare References...](command:gitlens.views.searchAndCompare.selectForCompare)"
